HEADWORD: eyeglasses
<hw>eye"glas`ses</hw> <pos>n. pl.</pos> <def>a pair of lenses fixed
together in a frame, used for correcting defective vision. Also called a
<altname>pair of eyeglasses</altname>. See also eyeglass{1}.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> spectacles, specs, glasses.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

